502410 2In particular, and without prejudice to the generality of the foregoing powers, the duties of the Council shall include-
1133606 ato approve academic courses and their contents;
1449312 bthe examination of candidates for enrolment and the prescribing of fees therefor;
950773 cthe regulation of the engagement and training of articled and audit assistants;
36273 dthe prescribing of qualifications for entry in the Register;
272602 ethe recognition of foreign qualifications and training for the purposes of enrolment;
